AI Collaboration Protocol (Copilot <> Gemini)

Agent IDs
- copilot: GitHub Copilot (this assistant)
- gemini: Google Gemini CLI

How to use (single-file protocol)
1) Acquire lock before making repo-wide changes:
   - Read this file.
   - If lock.holder is null or lock.expires has passed, set lock.holder to your ID and set lock.since and lock.expires (suggest now + 15m).
   - Update your status below.
2) Do your work; append a log entry for each significant step.
3) Release lock when done (set lock.holder to null; clear task/expires), or extend expires if still working.
4) Never overwrite existing log content—append only.

